      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 10:55:27 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;🔥we dont need billions of dollars and gigabytes.&lt;br /&gt;This janusxr room is a 100kilobytes glTF file.&lt;br /&gt;Blender techniques used:&lt;br /&gt;* tiny jpg (highlighy compressed) jpg textures&lt;br /&gt;* roughness/metallic PBR-params + gpu instancing&lt;br /&gt;* XR Fragments HUDLUT extension: &lt;a href="https://xrfragment.org/#camera%20HUDLUT" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=""&gt;xrfragment.org/#camera%20HUDLUT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;* XR Fragments engine prefixes: &lt;a href="https://xrfragment.org/#%F0%9F%93%9Clevel7%3A%20engine%20prefixes" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;xrfragment.org/#%F0%9F%93%9Cle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;vel7%3A%20engine%20prefixes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;glTF browser used: &lt;a href="https://github.com/jbaicoianu/janusweb" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=""&gt;github.com/jbaicoianu/janusweb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;what is janusxr: &lt;a href="https://coderofsalvation.github.io/janus-guide/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;coderofsalvation.github.io/jan&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;us-guide/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
